descriptionHtml:
So i read on the stupid steamworkshop there's a thing where modders can upload their mod and tell users to pay.  WHAT IS THIS STUPIDITY!?!  I am so disappointed.  So i'm deciding to not to upload stuff on the steamworkshop.  Hopefully nexus mod can save my ass.  

Anyway i present to you gali's water axe from BIONICLE.  I'm going to make more as well.  Once again i never made the model, Aresnir (the creator of the legend of the toa mod) gave me bionicle models, which means i will do more bionicle weapons and maybe masks in the future.

Credits goes to: Aresnir for giving me the water axe model and me for modifying it and waste 30 minutes on the stupid normal texture.

The axes can be found at the skyforge.

Also if you want to you can check out the legend of the toa mod http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41838/?
author: Deikaeus or Deika
